summary: Nick Diaz, a veteran UFC fighter from Stockton, is set to make his long-awaited return to the octagon by the end of the year, according to Cesar Gracie. name: Starlink
summary: Starlink, a satellite-based internet service from SpaceX, has faced various developments. Russia has been actively blocking the service in Ukraine, while SpaceX CEO Elon Musk has confirmed a brief outage of the service. The price of Starlink has also been increased, sparking reactions on Reddit. Concerns have arisen in China regarding the potential use of Starlink in a Taiwan contingency. SpaceX has continued to launch Starlink satellites, including on the fifth anniversary of its first dedicated Starlink flight. Following a brief outage, Starlink has resumed operations. SpaceX has also successfully launched 23 Starlink satellites from Florida.

summary: Olympic gymnast Gabby Douglas has unfortunately ended her bid to compete in the 2024 Paris Olympics due to an ankle injury. name: Conference League
summary: In a thrilling Europa Conference League final, Greek side Olympiacos emerged victorious over Fiorentina in extra time. The match, held in Athens under a massive security operation, saw a dramatic goal from El Kaabi secure the title for Olympiacos. The win marks a historic moment for Greek football, as Olympiacos becomes the first Greek team to win a major European trophy. The victory also grants Olympiacos qualification for next season's Europa League. Fiorentina, despite a valiant effort, fell short in their pursuit of the trophy.

name: Dallas Mavericks
summary: The Dallas Mavericks have taken a commanding 3-1 lead in the Western Conference Finals after defeating the Minnesota Timberwolves 116-107 in Game 4. Luka Doncic and Kyrie Irving led the way for the Mavericks, each scoring 33 points. The Timberwolves won Game 4, thanks to a 119-109 victory, but the Mavericks are still in a strong position to advance to the NBA Finals. The two teams will face off in Game 5 on Thursday, May 25, with the Mavericks looking to close out the series and the Timberwolves aiming to extend it to a sixth game.
